Intersnack Group GmbH & Co. KG, a European player, has a portfolio of well-known brands such as Chio and funny-frisch, providing consumers with a variety of extruded snack options. Kellogg Company, a global leader in breakfast cereals, has expanded its presence in the extruded snacks market with products like Cheez-It and Pringles, leveraging its strong distribution network and brand recognition. Old Dutch Foods, Inc., a Canadian company, focuses on high-quality ingredients and innovative flavors in its extruded snack offerings to maintain a loyal customer base.

